Paths address values inside the parsed JSON.

|!Form           |!Meaning                                |!Where allowed       |
|`key`           |object property access                  |anywhere             |
|`key.subkey`    |chained property                        |anywhere             |
|`key[0]`        |concrete array index                    |anywhere             |
|`key[*]`        |iterate every array element             |only in `records`    |
|`a.b[0].c.d`    |mixed access                            |anywhere             |
|`a[*].b[*].c`   |nested iteration                        |only in `records`    |
|`..`            |step up one ancestor scope              |only in binding tokens (§5.4) |

